{
  "name": "funding_rate_reversion_v1_grid_v3_refine",
  "description": "Funding Rate Reversion v3 refine around the best v2 short row. Narrower bounded sweep around EMA 89 / ext 0.3% / TP 2.5x ATR profile to test whether the small v2 edge is stable or just noise.",
  "cache_only": true,
  "command": [
    "{python}",
